      <title>秘密银行评级反映美国监管机构对处理风险的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/secret-bank-ratings-show-us-regulator-s-concern-on-handling-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，美国一家重要监管机构私下发现，其监管的半数主要银行对从网络攻击到员工失误等一系列潜在风险缺乏充分了解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/secret-bank-ratings-show-us-regulator-s-concern-on-handling-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 16:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
