      <title>标普 500 指数的下一步上涨取决于受创股票的复仇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/s-p-500-s-next-leg-up-hinges-on-battered-stocks-getting-revenge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着交易员对近期降息的信心越来越强，除大型科技公司之外的股市各个角落都在大幅上涨——这引发了人们对新一轮牛市即将来临的希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/s-p-500-s-next-leg-up-hinges-on-battered-stocks-getting-revenge</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
