      <title>遭受停电打击的伊拉克开始通过新线路进口土耳其电力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/blackout-hit-iraq-begins-importing-turkish-power-with-new-line</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其和伊拉克之间规划了20年的一条输电线路开始运营，有可能帮助这个产油阿拉伯国家解决严重的停电问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/blackout-hit-iraq-begins-importing-turkish-power-with-new-line</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 11:24:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
